articles.headline: Lawrence on confrontations with Texans: We won't be bullied
articles.description: Trevor Lawrence said the Jaguars were not going to be bullied when asked about the chippy nature of Sunday's win over the division-rival Texans.

articles.headline: Cowboys WR CeeDee Lamb ruled out vs. Bears with ankle injury
articles.description: Cowboys receiver CeeDee Lamb twisted an ankle on a carry in the first quarter and won't return at Chicago.

articles.headline: Isaiah Rodgers scores 2 defensive touchdowns as Vikings roll
articles.description: Minnesota Vikings cornerback Isaiah Rodgers, in his first season as a full-time starter, became the first player in league history to score two defensive touchdowns and force two fumbles in a game, capping his club's 48-10 win over the Cincinnati Bengals.

images.name: Isaiah Rodgers (Sept. 21, 2025) [1296x729]
images.caption: Vikings cornerback Isaiah Rodgers celebrates one of his two defensive return touchdowns Sunday -- both coming in the first half.

images.name: Isaiah Rodgers scores his 2nd defensive TD for Vikings
images.caption: Isaiah Rodgers forces a fumble and comes away with the ball for his second touchdown of the game for the Vikings.

articles.headline: Cardinals' James Conner carted off with ankle injury
articles.description: Cardinals running back James Conner was ruled out of the rest of Sunday's game against the 49ers after getting carted off the field with a right ankle injury.

articles.headline: San Francisco 49ers DE Nick Bosa leaves with knee injury
articles.description: San Francisco 49ers defensive end Nick Bosa, who posted two sacks, eight pressures and 15 tackles in the first two weeks, will not return to Sunday's game against the Arizona Cardinals after suffering a knee injury in the first quarter at Levi's Stadium.
